><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1770371838024" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1770371838024" data-resolution="3000x3000" style=""><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/1c56a9a2-efe6-4182-b007-08ad2d2ab62e/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/Image%2091.webp" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1000" natural-height="600" width="1000" height="600" loading="lazy" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1770371270532" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1770371270532" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000">7. Praktisch portioniert für Tee Rituale (150 ml)</font></h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1770371312382" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1770371312382" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Ideal für Tee, Kräuteraufgüsse oder Matcha: genau die Größe, die zu bewussten Pausen passt – klein, fein, besonders.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data